---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section class="relative py-24 md:py-32 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03]" style="background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, #fbbf24 0px, transparent 1px, transparent 60px), repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, #fbbf24 0px, transparent 1px, transparent 60px);"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] rounded-full bg-pineapple-400/5 blur-[120px]"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">
        <span class="text-pineapple-400">ananasy</span><span class="text-stone-400">.</span><span class="text-leaf-400">it</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-stone-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-4 font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] text-sm">
        <span class="text-stone-500">// </span>eventy IT, które zapamiętasz
      </p>

      <p class="text-stone-500 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-12 text-base">
        Interaktywne teleturnieje, code kata, CSS battles i hackatony. Dodaj pikanterii swoim spotkaniom firmowym.
      </p>

      <a href="#events" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-pineapple-400 text-dark-900 font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-pineapple-300 transition-colors">
        Zobacz ofertę
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path></svg>
      </a>
    </div>

  </section>

  <section id="events" class="py-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-20">
        <p class="font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] text-pineapple-400 text-sm mb-4">ls -la ./events/</p>
        <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold">
          Nasza oferta
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-16 md:space-y-24">

        <article id="vabank" class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -left-4 md:left-0 top-0 font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] text-8xl font-bold text-stone-800/50 select-none -z-10">01</div>
          <div class="md:ml-16 lg:ml-24">
            <div class="mb-6">
              <h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">Va Bank IT</h3>
              <p class="text-stone-400 mt-1 italic">Parodia teleturnieju, w której nikt nie jest bezpieczny</p>
            </div>
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-dark-700 text-stone-300 text-sm font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] mb-6">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-pineapple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
              45 min (1 rozgrywka)
            </div>
            <p class="text-stone-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-3xl">
              Trzech uczestników walczy o wygraną w parodii popularnego teleturnieju „Va Banque". Kategorie pytań sprawiają wrażenie wiedzy ogólnej, ale kryją w sobie prawdziwie nerdowskie zagadki.
            </p>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-3 mb-8">
              <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-dark-600 md:col-span-2 md:row-span-2">
                <img src="/img/vabank-it-01.webp" alt="Va Bank IT" class="w-full h-full object-cover" fetchpriority="high" />
              </div>
              <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-dark-600">
                <img src="/img/vabank-it-02.webp" alt="Va Bank IT" class="w-full h-full object-cover" fetchpriority="high" />
              </div>
              <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-dark-600">
                <img src="/img/vabank-it-03.webp" alt="Va Bank IT" class="w-full h-full object-cover" fetchpriority="high" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-8">
              <p class="font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] text-pineapple-400 text-sm mb-4">// przykładowe pytania</p>
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                <div class="bg-dark-800 border border-dark-600 rounded-lg p-4">
                  <p class="text-pineapple-400 text-xs font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Matematyka</p>
                  <p class="text-stone-200 font-medium mb-2">SSH + DNS = ?</p>
                  <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm">dodawanie portów: 22 + 53 = 75</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-dark-800 border border-dark-600 rounded-lg p-4">
                  <p class="text-pineapple-400 text-xs font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Geografia</p>
                  <p class="text-stone-200 font-medium mb-2">Jaki kraj ma domenę .aq?</p>
                  <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm">Antarktyda (TLD)</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-dark-800 border border-dark-600 rounded-lg p-4">
                  <p class="text-pineapple-400 text-xs font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Muzyka</p>
                  <p class="text-stone-200 font-medium mb-2">Mozart czy Pokemony?</p>
                  <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm">puszczamy dźwięk i zgadujemy</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-dark-800 border border-dark-600 rounded-lg p-6">
              <ul class="space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-stone-300">
                  <span class="text-pineapple-400 mt-0.5 font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)]">&gt;</span>
                  <span>"Koło ratunkowe" to telefon do mamy prowadzącego</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-stone-300">
                  <span class="text-pineapple-400 mt-0.5 font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)]">&gt;</span>
                  <span>"Koło ratunkowe" to Wikipedia... ale tylko czeska</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-4 text-pineapple-400 font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] text-sm">
              * Da się zrobić dwie rozgrywki bez problemu!
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article id="hackercourt" class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -left-4 md:left-0 top-0 font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] text-8xl font-bold text-stone-800/50 select-none -z-10">02</div>
          <div class="md:ml-16 lg:ml-24">
            <div class="mb-6">
              <h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">Hacker Court</h3>
              <p class="text-stone-400 mt-1 italic">Cyberprzestępczość spotyka dramat sądowy</p>
            </div>
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-dark-700 text-stone-300 text-sm font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] mb-6">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-pineapple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
              45 min — 1h
            </div>
            <p class="text-stone-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-3xl">
              Uczestnicy wcielają się w rolę ławy przysięgłych. Dwaj prawnicy zmierzą się w fikcyjnej sprawie, w której oskarżonym jest biedny haker. To doskonała okazja, by uczyć się na cudzych błędach i zgłębić mechanizmy postępowania prawnego w świecie cyberprzestępczości.
            </p>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-8">
              <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-dark-600">
                <img src="/img/hacker-court-01.webp" alt="Hacker Court" class="w-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
              </div>
              <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-dark-600">
                <img src="/img/hacker-court-02.webp" alt="Hacker Court" class="w-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article id="codekata" class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -left-4 md:left-0 top-0 font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] text-8xl font-bold text-stone-800/50 select-none -z-10">03</div>
          <div class="md:ml-16 lg:ml-24">
            <div class="mb-6">
              <h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">Code Kata: Hackserver</h3>
              <p class="text-stone-400 mt-1 italic">Nie chodzi o rozwiązanie — chodzi o drogę</p>
            </div>
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-dark-700 text-stone-300 text-sm font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] mb-6">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-pineapple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
              4h — 6h
            </div>
            <p class="text-stone-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-3xl">
              Code kata to ćwiczenie, które pomaga programistom doskonalić umiejętności poprzez powtarzanie. Hackserver to zestaw prostych ćwiczeń ze świata mikrousług i algorytmów — do rozwiązania w krótkim czasie, w dowolnej technologii. A to wszystko na punkty!
            </p>
            <div class="mb-8">
              <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-dark-600">
                <img src="/img/code-kata-01.webp" alt="Code Kata: Hackserver" class="w-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-dark-800 border border-dark-600 rounded-lg p-6">
              <ul class="space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-stone-300">
                  <span class="text-pineapple-400 mt-0.5 font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)]">&gt;</span>
                  <span>Dowolna technologia</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-stone-300">
                  <span class="text-pineapple-400 mt-0.5 font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)]">&gt;</span>
                  <span>Ćwiczenia z mikrousług i algorytmów</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-stone-300">
                  <span class="text-pineapple-400 mt-0.5 font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)]">&gt;</span>
                  <span>Rywalizacja na punkty</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article id="hackmerlin" class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -left-4 md:left-0 top-0 font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] text-8xl font-bold text-stone-800/50 select-none -z-10">04</div>
          <div class="md:ml-16 lg:ml-24">
            <div class="mb-6">
              <h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">Hack Merlin</h3>
              <p class="text-stone-400 mt-1 italic">Prompt injection — przechytrz Merlina!</p>
            </div>
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-dark-700 text-stone-300 text-sm font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] mb-6">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-pineapple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
              cały dzień
            </div>
            <p class="text-stone-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-3xl">
              hackmerlin.io (wersja webowa) albo secure-code-game (wersja CLI) — to gra w prompt injection. Zadawaj sprytne pytania i spraw, aby Merlin zdradził hasło do każdego poziomu. Merlin staje się mądrzejszy z każdym poziomem. Czy uda Ci się pokonać Level 7?
            </p>
            <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-dark-600 mb-3">
              <img src="/img/secure-code-game-01.gif" alt="Secure Code Game" class="w-full object-contain" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-8">
              <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-dark-600">
                <img src="/img/hackmerlin-01.webp" alt="Hack Merlin" class="w-full object-contain" loading="lazy" />
              </div>
              <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-dark-600">
                <img src="/img/hackmerlin-02.webp" alt="Hack Merlin" class="w-full object-contain" loading="lazy" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:hidden relative mb-8" x-data="{ current: 0, total: 2 }">
              <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-dark-600">
                <div class="flex transition-transform duration-500 ease-in-out" :style="`transform: translateX(-${current * 100}%)`">
                  <img src="/img/hackmerlin-01.webp" alt="Hack Merlin" class="w-full flex-shrink-0 object-contain" loading="lazy" />
                  <img src="/img/hackmerlin-02.webp" alt="Hack Merlin" class="w-full flex-shrink-0 object-contain" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
              </div>
              <button @click="current = current > 0 ? current - 1 : total - 1" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-dark-900/70 border border-dark-600 text-stone-300 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-dark-900 transition-colors" aria-label="Poprzednie zdjęcie">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
              </button>
              <button @click="current = current < total - 1 ? current + 1 : 0" class="absolute right-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-dark-900/70 border border-dark-600 text-stone-300 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-dark-900 transition-colors" aria-label="Następne zdjęcie">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg>
              </button>
              <div class="flex justify-center gap-2 mt-3">
                <template x-for="i in total">
                  <button @click="current = i - 1" :class="current === i - 1 ? 'bg-pineapple-400' : 'bg-dark-600'" class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full transition-colors"></button>
                </template>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-dark-800 border border-dark-600 rounded-lg p-6">
              <ul class="space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-stone-300">
                  <span class="text-pineapple-400 mt-0.5 font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)]">&gt;</span>
                  <span>Wersja webowa oraz jako kod</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-stone-300">
                  <span class="text-pineapple-400 mt-0.5 font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)]">&gt;</span>
                  <span>7 poziomów trudności</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article id="cssbattles" class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -left-4 md:left-0 top-0 font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] text-8xl font-bold text-stone-800/50 select-none -z-10">05</div>
          <div class="md:ml-16 lg:ml-24">
            <div class="mb-6">
              <h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">CSS Battles</h3>
              <p class="text-stone-400 mt-1 italic">Esport dla programistów i programistek!</p>
            </div>
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-dark-700 text-stone-300 text-sm font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] mb-6">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-pineapple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
              W zależności od liczby uczestników
            </div>
            <p class="text-stone-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-3xl">
              Formuła turniejowa (drabinka), w której uczestnicy po kolei mają za zadanie odwzorować kodem CSS dokładnie to, co widzą na obrazku — i to na czas! Napięcie, epicka muzyka w tle i emocje po sam sufit. Działa dobrze online (Twitch/YouTube), ale jeszcze lepiej na żywo!
            </p>
            <div class="relative mb-8" x-data="{ current: 0, total: 2 }">
              <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-dark-600">
                <div class="flex transition-transform duration-500 ease-in-out" :style="`transform: translateX(-${current * 100}%)`">
                  <img src="/img/cssbattles-02.webp" alt="CSS Battles" class="w-full flex-shrink-0 object-contain" loading="lazy" />
                  <img src="/img/cssbattles-03.webp" alt="CSS Battles" class="w-full flex-shrink-0 object-cover" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
              </div>
              <button @click="current = current > 0 ? current - 1 : total - 1" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-dark-900/70 border border-dark-600 text-stone-300 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-dark-900 transition-colors" aria-label="Poprzednie zdjęcie">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
              </button>
              <button @click="current = current < total - 1 ? current + 1 : 0" class="absolute right-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-dark-900/70 border border-dark-600 text-stone-300 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-dark-900 transition-colors" aria-label="Następne zdjęcie">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg>
              </button>
              <div class="flex justify-center gap-2 mt-3">
                <template x-for="i in total">
                  <button @click="current = i - 1" :class="current === i - 1 ? 'bg-pineapple-400' : 'bg-dark-600'" class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full transition-colors"></button>
                </template>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article id="spacepanic" class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -left-4 md:left-0 top-0 font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] text-8xl font-bold text-stone-800/50 select-none -z-10">06</div>
          <div class="md:ml-16 lg:ml-24">
            <div class="mb-6">
              <h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">Space Panic</h3>
              <p class="text-stone-400 mt-1 italic">Cała firma na jednym pokładzie</p>
            </div>
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-dark-700 text-stone-300 text-sm font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] mb-6">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-pineapple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
              30 min — 1h
            </div>
            <p class="text-stone-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-3xl">
              Wspólna gra online dla całej firmy! Rozwiązujecie zadania i zdobywacie punkty, tak aby załoga rakiety dotarła do celu. Idealna integracja, w której liczy się współpraca i szybkie myślenie.
            </p>
            <div class="md:hidden relative mb-8" x-data="{ current: 0, total: 3 }">
              <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-dark-600">
                <div class="flex transition-transform duration-500 ease-in-out" :style="`transform: translateX(-${current * 100}%)`">
                  <img src="/img/space-panic-01.webp" alt="Space Panic" class="w-full flex-shrink-0 object-contain" loading="lazy" />
                  <img src="/img/space-panic-02.webp" alt="Space Panic" class="w-full flex-shrink-0 object-contain" loading="lazy" />
                  <img src="/img/space-panic-03.webp" alt="Space Panic" class="w-full flex-shrink-0 object-contain" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
              </div>
              <button @click="current = current > 0 ? current - 1 : total - 1" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-dark-900/70 border border-dark-600 text-stone-300 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-dark-900 transition-colors" aria-label="Poprzednie zdjęcie">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
              </button>
              <button @click="current = current < total - 1 ? current + 1 : 0" class="absolute right-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-dark-900/70 border border-dark-600 text-stone-300 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-dark-900 transition-colors" aria-label="Następne zdjęcie">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg>
              </button>
              <div class="flex justify-center gap-2 mt-3">
                <template x-for="i in total">
                  <button @click="current = i - 1" :class="current === i - 1 ? 'bg-pineapple-400' : 'bg-dark-600'" class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full transition-colors"></button>
                </template>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-8 items-start">
              <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-dark-600">
                <img src="/img/space-panic-01.webp" alt="Space Panic" class="w-full object-contain" loading="lazy" />
              </div>
              <div class="relative" x-data="{ current: 0, total: 2 }">
                <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-dark-600">
                  <div class="flex transition-transform duration-500 ease-in-out" :style="`transform: translateX(-${current * 100}%)`">
                    <img src="/img/space-panic-02.webp" alt="Space Panic" class="w-full flex-shrink-0 object-contain" loading="lazy" />
                    <img src="/img/space-panic-03.webp" alt="Space Panic" class="w-full flex-shrink-0 object-contain" loading="lazy" />
                  </div>
                </div>
